text: Tiffany Celine Ho (born 6 January 1998) is an Australian badminton player. She was the champion at the 2016 Oceania Championships in the women's doubles event partnered with Jennifer Tam, and at the same year, she claimed her first international title at the Waikato International tournament in the women's doubles event.
